	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just one thing to add to this. Practice grouping. A lot.&nbsp;&nbsp;Come lvl 46, when you get those plane shift spells, you're going to want to be the kind of wizard that people can rely on, otherwise you won't get to use them much =)<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
