	   <tr><td colspan=2>I also feel that nuking mid-way through a mob's HP is best because I have quite OFTEN ended up casting that final blow after it's death. The problem is that casting does take time and with a full group also fighting, if you wait too long you're going to miss it and just waste a lot of mana.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
